Usign IconGrid with ToolManager
*******************************

If you already tried using IconGrid, you have probably noticed that it
is quite a lot of work typing all the filenames of the icons which
should be positioned. To simplify this a lot, I would advise you to get
StefanBecker's ToolManager. With this program, you can add IconGrid to
your Workbench's Tools-Menu. Aligning icons is then as easy as
selecting them with extended selection directly on Workbench and using
the Tools-Menu entry.

You might even want to enter IconGrid several times into ToolManager
with different GRIDSIZE arguments.


@EndNode

